metadata.name: Hydrangea
metadata.description: The hydrangea flower embodies the delicate beauty and grace of a woman. Her large, fluffy blooms are a reflection of a gentle and nurturing spirit, radiating warmth and kindness. The intricate texture and layers of the flower symbolize the depth of her character, revealing a complexity that is both intriguing and fascinating. As the hydrangea can change colors depending on its surroundings, this woman is adaptable and resilient, able to thrive in any environment. Her rich symbolism of love, gratitude, and abundance inspires joy and contentment, making her a true treasure to those around her.
